name: AURORA
description: Flame fractal generated landscape. Aurora is one of Rodstoulle's fractal landscape paintings done between 2017 to 2018. These paintings, which consists on a myriad of separated collections under this aesthetic such as Guarapari, Landscape Studies #001, Landscape Studies #002, Magic Mountains, Sunset fields, and more, are all algorithmically created based on the artist years of fractal studies. Aurora is a printable version with 60cm x 42cm (23,62 inches x 16,53 inches) dimension. All primary buyers will be granted the printable version for life. Secondary buyers have authorization to have the print distributed to them.
